WEBVTT

00:08.000 --> 00:11.000
[Ray] Previously on
Ray Donovan...

00:11.000 --> 00:12.959
I'm afraid to go home.

00:12.959 --> 00:14.834
I'm taking my things, I'm taking
my dog and I'm leaving.

00:14.834 --> 00:17.458
- Give me my dog!
- [dog barks]

00:17.458 --> 00:20.041
Over my dead body
you take our dog.

00:20.041 --> 00:22.000
[Doug] She's pretty special,
isn't she?

00:22.000 --> 00:23.166
[Ray] What?

00:23.166 --> 00:26.041
I said, she's pretty special,
isn't she?

00:26.041 --> 00:28.375
I don't know what arrangements
you made with my son,

00:28.375 --> 00:30.166
but my services
aren't included.

00:30.166 --> 00:30.917
- So what do I owe you?
- I've been getting

00:30.917 --> 00:33.583
some excellent feedback on this

00:33.583 --> 00:36.166
- little film that I wrote.
- Four Leaf?

00:36.166 --> 00:39.250
One of his top-notch writers
to help spruce it up.

00:39.250 --> 00:43.041
Jay White ain't making Michael
into a black veteran in Harlem.

00:43.041 --> 00:44.917
Wallet, cell phone
and your fuckin' bag.

00:44.917 --> 00:47.917
You g--
[grunts] Ohh!

00:47.917 --> 00:49.709
[Bunchy]
They robbed me, Pop.

00:49.709 --> 00:52.375
My settlement money.
They took it all.

00:52.375 --> 00:54.792
You want your money back,
you don't wanna ID me.

00:54.792 --> 00:57.333
You gonna fuckin' help me?

00:57.333 --> 01:00.125
Your mother's expecting me.

01:00.125 --> 01:00.875
Mom!

01:00.875 --> 01:05.291
Did you meet my step-son?

01:05.291 --> 01:07.667
- Who?
- George, when you came in.

01:08.792 --> 01:11.208
- Yeah.
- [Terry] My brother's wife--

01:11.208 --> 01:14.125
the thoughts I had
and the things I done.

01:14.125 --> 01:16.083
Did she take her own life?

01:18.500 --> 01:20.250
I gotta say something.

01:20.250 --> 01:22.875
I know, honey.

01:24.625 --> 01:26.709
[Terry] It was me that
gave her the drugs.

01:26.709 --> 01:29.333
I was in the room,
helping her do it.

01:31.250 --> 01:32.250
[thud]

01:39.417 --> 01:42.417
♪ somber music ♪

01:42.417 --> 01:47.333
♪♪♪

01:59.750 --> 02:00.375
[groans] Ah.

02:07.959 --> 02:10.125
[liquor pouring]

02:10.792 --> 02:13.125
I'll let you have
that one.

02:14.792 --> 02:16.750
Fuck you.

02:18.417 --> 02:21.417
You know what
you don't like about me?

02:21.417 --> 02:23.875
I'm the only person on this
Earth who's got the balls

02:23.875 --> 02:26.083
to tell you the fuckin' truth.

02:29.875 --> 02:33.166
Now you listen to me, Raymond.

02:33.166 --> 02:35.959
It was what she fuckin' wanted.

02:37.250 --> 02:39.458
It was her choice.

02:39.458 --> 02:41.959
Not yours.

02:42.792 --> 02:45.041
Don't you see
what you're doing?

02:45.041 --> 02:46.667
Bridget ran away to New York.

02:46.667 --> 02:51.500
Conor--he's joining
the fuckin' Marines.

02:51.500 --> 02:53.458
And that's all because of you.

02:55.834 --> 02:58.625
I love you, Raymond.

02:58.625 --> 03:03.166
But do yourself a favor and
look in the fuckin' mirror.

03:03.166 --> 03:05.375
Because you're pushing us
all away.

03:19.667 --> 03:21.667
♪ somber music ♪

03:21.667 --> 03:27.583
