04:12.458 --> 04:14.792
[horn blares, tires screech]

04:14.792 --> 04:20.709
♪♪♪

04:49.542 --> 04:51.875
You lookin' for something?

04:56.625 --> 04:59.250
You want some company?

05:06.625 --> 05:09.542
[cell phone rings]

05:14.875 --> 05:16.959
Yeah.

05:16.959 --> 05:18.750
