06:09.542 --> 06:11.792
[Mickey, muttering] Oh, uh--

06:11.792 --> 06:14.709
- [Mickey] Ah, yeah.
- [Daryll] Okay.

06:14.709 --> 06:18.291
Okay, okay. Here, come on.
Help me lift him.

06:18.291 --> 06:22.166
We get caught for this--
lethal injection at San Quentin.

06:22.166 --> 06:25.083
- Fuckin' telling ya.
- And I said help me lift him.

06:25.083 --> 06:26.375
