06:26.375 --> 06:27.125
He's a very large man.

06:27.125 --> 06:29.709
Jesus. [grunts]

06:29.709 --> 06:31.625
[cell phone rings]

06:31.625 --> 06:32.917
What now?

06:32.917 --> 06:35.375
[ringing]

06:35.375 --> 06:38.667
- Yeah.
- [Antoine] D-Squared.

06:38.667 --> 06:40.709
- What?
- I'm sorry, Daryll Donovan?

06:40.709 --> 06:41.333
- Yeah.
- Hey, what's happening?

06:41.333 --> 06:43.583
- It's Triple-A.
- Who?

06:43.583 --> 06:45.834
Antoine A'Shawn Anderson.

06:45.834 --> 06:47.959
Oh, yeah, yeah.
What's up, my man?

06:47.959 --> 06:50.041
Hey, look, I finished
your father's movie script,

06:50.041 --> 06:52.333
and I was hoping that you two
could come down

06:52.333 --> 06:55.250
to Pacific tomorrow
so we can go over some shit.

06:55.250 --> 06:56.709
Okay, yeah.
That's what's up, man.

06:56.709 --> 06:57.500
Yeah, should--
shouldn't be a problem.

06:57.500 --> 07:00.250
All right.
I'll see you tomorrow.

07:00.250 --> 07:02.417
- [panting]
- Who was that?

07:02.417 --> 07:03.583
What?

07:03.583 --> 07:05.208
Who was that?

07:05.208 --> 07:07.458
Oh, uh, Triple-A.
Uh, Jay White's guy.

07:07.458 --> 07:08.583
Yeah? What'd he want?

07:08.583 --> 07:11.542
Tomorrow he wants you
to come by Pacific

07:11.542 --> 07:13.834
so y'all can talk about
the movie.

07:13.834 --> 07:15.792
