and not me?

07:15.792 --> 07:17.125
I don't know, Pop.
Maybe you don't have a signal

07:17.125 --> 07:19.792
on your phone.

07:21.917 --> 07:23.667
I got, like, four bars.

07:23.667 --> 07:25.500
Jesus, Mickey,
you're killing me.

07:25.500 --> 07:27.208
Help me spin the legs around.

07:27.208 --> 07:29.041
The legs are all right.
You gotta turn the body.

07:29.041 --> 07:30.750
You gotta turn the shoulders.

07:30.750 --> 07:32.250
- [Mickey] Good.
- [grunts]

07:32.250 --> 07:33.750
Keep going, keep going.

07:33.750 --> 07:35.583
He's starting to move
on his own, here.

07:35.583 --> 07:38.542
See? Let him go, he's slidin'.
He's slidin'.

07:40.375 --> 07:43.500
♪ dark music ♪

07:43.500 --> 07:45.625
[Mickey] Yeah.
There he goes, there he goes.

07:45.625 --> 07:49.291
♪♪♪

07:49.291 --> 07:52.125
Rest in peace, you prick.

07:52.125 --> 07:54.792
[metallic clinking]

07:54.792 --> 07:57.792
