09:27.208 --> 09:31.166
- [Bridget] Here. [murmurs]
- [Smitty, whimpering]

09:37.375 --> 09:41.542
[Bridget breathing hard]

09:48.458 --> 09:50.750
I saw my dad

09:50.750 --> 09:55.125
at the Fulton Street Station.

09:55.125 --> 09:58.709
He whispered in my ear.

09:58.709 --> 10:02.750
Just like this: [whispering]
Everything's gonna be okay.

10:05.083 --> 10:07.792
[whimpers]
But it's not gonna be okay.

10:07.792 --> 10:09.250
My dad died
when I was a kid, I--

10:09.250 --> 10:12.000
[shaky inhale]

10:12.000 --> 10:13.583
