10:13.583 --> 10:16.166
[whispers] Hey...
you're okay.

10:16.166 --> 10:18.583
Hey, pretty.

10:18.583 --> 10:20.750
[small laugh]

10:20.750 --> 10:24.875
♪♪♪

10:36.417 --> 10:38.417
[engine humming,
vehicle approaches]

10:38.417 --> 10:40.750
[man] That's him.
Slow down, slow down!

10:40.750 --> 10:42.500
