to do with this.

12:46.417 --> 12:49.875
I hope you don't
mind me saying, but...

12:49.875 --> 12:52.834
you left the boy
when he was 13 and...

12:52.834 --> 12:57.250
now he's got a chance
at the big time,

12:57.250 --> 12:59.542
you're coming out the woodwork.

13:01.667 --> 13:03.417
- See how that looks?
- It's not like that.

13:03.417 --> 13:06.792
You don't understand.

13:06.792 --> 13:10.917
I'm his father. Not you.

13:10.917 --> 13:12.250
That's true.

13:12.250 --> 13:15.500
Well...

13:15.500 --> 13:19.583
here's how it is:

13:19.583 --> 13:23.291
you hurt the kid,

13:23.291 --> 13:25.166
and I'll hurt you.

13:27.458 --> 13:30.166
You got that?

13:32.333 --> 13:34.041
Now fuck off.

13:38.291 --> 13:40.333
♪ soft, edgy music ♪

13:40.333 --> 13:46.166
