14:23.834 --> 14:26.583
Hey, don't worry, man.
We're gonna find

14:26.583 --> 14:30.291
this buried treasure,
and we get our big pimpin' on.

14:30.291 --> 14:31.834
- All right?
- All right.

14:31.834 --> 14:35.625
- [Bunchy] Come on.
- Hoo-hoo!

14:54.417 --> 14:56.291
[blows softly]

15:02.583 --> 15:05.125
[phone rings]

15:06.542 --> 15:09.500
[ringing]

15:11.375 --> 15:12.875
[beep]

15:12.875 --> 15:14.000
[phone thunks down]

15:22.500 --> 15:25.875
[distant voices,
traffic sounds]

15:32.250 --> 15:33.375
[footstep]

15:34.417 --> 15:38.083
People as sad as us
shouldn't live so high up.

15:43.583 --> 15:46.709
[phone rings]

15:54.834 --> 15:56.458
[continues ringing]

15:56.458 --> 15:57.750
[beep]

15:57.750 --> 15:59.041
Yeah?

15:59.041 --> 16:01.792
Turn on Stalkerazzi.

16:06.917 --> 16:09.250
[TV chatter]

16:09.250 --> 16:10.542
[channels changing]

16:10.542 --> 16:13.875
[Marty] Please tell me that
Natalie James is still holed up

16:13.875 --> 16:16.709
with our super Hollywood
fixer Ray Donovan.

16:16.709 --> 16:21.166
I mean, this is a code
red hot situation, everyone.

16:21.166 --> 16:22.125
It is, Marty, and yes,
they're still holed up.

16:22.125 --> 16:24.625
And now there's
rumors circulating

16:24.625 --> 16:26.583
she might have
a bun in the oven.

16:26.583 --> 16:27.834
[Marty] Stop it! Stop!
I can't take this in one day.

16:27.834 --> 16:30.834
I can't take it.
Ray Donovan--

16:30.834 --> 16:33.917
♪ soft, edgy music ♪

16:33.917 --> 16:39.041
♪♪♪

16:50.792 --> 16:54.041
Where are you going?

16:57.500 --> 16:58.417
[door thuds closed]

16:58.417 --> 17:00.000
[Marty]
The mysterious Ray Donovan

17:00.000 --> 17:03.000
may be the--the baby daddy.

17:03.000 --> 17:05.166
[Sandy] I mean, maybe. We're
gonna find out soon enough.

17:05.166 --> 17:06.834
[Marty] Any guesses?
Any guesses?

17:06.834 --> 17:08.667
[Sandy] Um, 50/50 on the...

17:08.667 --> 17:11.750
I have no fuckin' idea
who that Dave Donovan guy is,

17:11.750 --> 17:12.500
but he's one
lucky motherfucker,

17:12.500 --> 17:14.333
am I right?

17:14.333 --> 17:17.500
I mean, it's kinda hard
going back to your right hand

17:17.500 --> 17:18.375
after doing that for a stretch.

17:18.375 --> 17:20.667
[Marty continues
indistinctly on TV]

17:20.667 --> 17:21.959
You know what I'm sayin'?

17:21.959 --> 17:24.166
[country music plays
in background]

17:24.166 --> 17:28.041
[Marty] Whatever this is,
there are, uh, many more

17:28.041 --> 17:30.417
layers to peel off
of this onion.

17:30.417 --> 17:32.166
- [dog whimpers]
- [Sandy] So maybe now

17:32.166 --> 17:33.250
this is out,
he's gonna wanna talk to us.

17:33.250 --> 17:35.250
[Marty] Ray talk?
That's never gonna happen.

17:35.250 --> 17:38.041
-  [Sandy]  Why?
-  [Marty]  I-I've known

17:38.041 --> 17:42.333
this guy...I don't know,
almost my entire career.

17:42.333 --> 17:44.875
Hey, hey, hey, hey! Hey!

17:44.875 --> 17:47.709
[country music continues,
muffled]

17:47.709 --> 17:51.709
