or Ventura areas.

18:14.291 --> 18:15.750
- [clattering]
- D--

18:18.667 --> 18:20.125
Ray--

18:20.125 --> 18:22.041
What are you fuckin' doing?!

18:22.041 --> 18:23.750
Oh, my fuckin' car!

18:23.750 --> 18:26.000
- Ray!
- Who gave you the story?

18:26.000 --> 18:28.166
