replacement parts are for this?

18:28.166 --> 18:30.083
No! No!
Oh, Jesus, Ray!

18:30.083 --> 18:33.458
I--I can't reveal my sources.

18:33.458 --> 18:34.583
No! No, no!

18:34.583 --> 18:35.417
Stop! Stop! Stop!

18:35.417 --> 18:37.750
Look, Ray,
I got it, I got it.

18:37.750 --> 18:39.750
It was your--your fixer friend.

18:39.750 --> 18:41.458
Vicky.

18:41.458 --> 18:42.291
V-Vicky Delgatti.

18:49.792 --> 18:50.417
[phone rings]

18:51.917 --> 18:54.458
- [beep]
- Yeah.

18:54.458 --> 18:56.417
- So, you sober?
- What?

18:56.417 --> 18:58.041
[Sam]
I called you last night.

18:58.041 --> 18:59.208
You hung up on me.

18:59.208 --> 18:59.917
You remember that?

18:59.917 --> 19:02.667
What do you want?

19:02.667 --> 19:04.458
George ran off with
the box of evidence.

19:04.458 --> 19:06.166
[Sam] I've been looking
for him all night.

19:06.166 --> 19:07.917
I'll find him.

19:09.333 --> 19:10.291
- [phone rings]
- Yeah?

19:10.291 --> 19:12.792
