get me his credit card info

19:16.166 --> 19:19.542
- and, uh, cell phone.
- Okay.

19:19.542 --> 19:22.041
And get me a home address
for Vicky Delgatti.

19:22.041 --> 19:23.125
All right. Do you want me
to pick her up?

19:23.125 --> 19:26.041
- No. Just get me her address.

19:26.041 --> 19:26.792
And get rid of those
fuckin' photographers

19:26.792 --> 19:29.000
outside my apartment.

19:29.000 --> 19:30.417
All right, will do.

19:30.417 --> 19:32.458
[phone beeps]

19:32.458 --> 19:35.500
♪ edgy music ♪

19:35.500 --> 19:36.959
