20:05.709 --> 20:08.000
So?

20:08.000 --> 20:10.583
So, Freddy, like,
didn't even spend a dime

20:10.583 --> 20:12.917
except for, like,
three grand on rock star.

20:12.917 --> 20:16.083
And a motorcycle.

20:20.166 --> 20:22.250
Hey, give me ten bucks.

20:23.375 --> 20:26.041
- What for?
- You'll see.

