a mask too, ET.

21:01.417 --> 21:03.375
I got a mask.

21:06.542 --> 21:08.834
[Dime-Bag] An old school bus.

21:10.542 --> 21:13.417
That's what+ I spent
my 15 large on.

21:14.583 --> 21:17.709
From the grocery store job.

21:17.709 --> 21:21.458
