and I drove that "cool" bus

21:21.458 --> 21:23.166
all the way down to
Venus, Texas

21:23.166 --> 21:24.000
with an Indian chick.

21:24.000 --> 21:28.583
Dots. Rainbow was her name.

21:28.583 --> 21:29.125
Why?

21:29.125 --> 21:31.375
Why not, more like.

21:31.375 --> 21:34.250
But w-w-why'd you wanna
go to Venus, Texas?

21:34.250 --> 21:36.500
Well, I wanted to go
to Paris, Texas--

21:36.500 --> 21:39.125
you know, check out
the Eiffel Tower and shit--

21:39.125 --> 21:41.792
but we got lost and, uh,
Rainbow, well...ha.

21:41.792 --> 21:44.542
She, uh...

21:44.542 --> 21:46.750
Well, never mind.

21:46.750 --> 21:48.583
[vehicle approaches]

21:49.542 --> 21:50.000
All right, you ready?

21:50.000 --> 21:52.000
Let's do this.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.500
[car door closes]

21:58.959 --> 22:00.583
[door hinges squeak]

22:02.417 --> 22:03.792
- [Bunchy] Oh, shit, it's a kid.
- Mom.

22:03.792 --> 22:04.625
We don't wanna
hurt you.

22:04.625 --> 22:06.667
[Dime-Bag]
Where's the diaper bag?

22:06.667 --> 22:08.291
